new-page: true

> *Nothingburger because it's WIP*

  - Dev, Metaquote Book

For more information on the politics of Valdara, see the "Library" page on the top left. If this is your first time playing the game, it is recommended that you read at least some of this information.

Difficulty affects starting resources and inter-party relations, as well as how difficult it is to change party advisors and ideology, reduce dissent, and increase relations.

