@SWPV-pase
title: Russian Social-Democratic Labor Party (Bolshevik)
choose-if: achievement_game_completed
unavailable-subtitle: Complete the game as one of the other parties first.

**Russian Social-Democratic Labor Party (Bolsheviks)** - The "majority" faction of the RSDLP is in fact the smaller party. Established by Vladimir Lenin's arguments in the various RSDLP congresses, the Bolsheviks are seen as more radical than the Mensheviks. They are a disciplined and centralized party of professional revolutionaries who aim to act as the vanguard of a proletarian revolution. During Lenin's exile, the remaining members in Russia have become more moderate and accommodating.

- @bolsheviks_2: Yes, I am a Bolshevik!
- @party_selection: No, select a different party.

